        <mxCell id="dll_note" value="Why a separate process?&#10;PyQt5 and ctranslate2 each bundle their own MSVCP140.dll on Windows.&#10;Loading both in one process caused an intermittent 0xC0000005&#10;access-violation crash — isolating faster-whisper into its own&#10;OS process sidesteps the conflict entirely." style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;size=14;align=left;spacingLeft=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1100" y="580" width="560" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

